Subject: Re: [HACKERS] PG+Cygwin Production Experience (was RE: Path to PostgreSQL
References: <E2870D8CE1CCD311BAF50008C71EDE8E01F74896@MAIL_EXCHANGE> <19035.1020952312@sss.pgh.pa.us>
