Received: [from pronto1.comm.mot.com (pronto1.comm.mot.com [173.6.1.22]) by pobox3.mot.com (MOT-pobox3 2.0) with ESMTP id MAA08146; Wed, 5 Jun 2002 12:31:08 -0700 (MST)]
